archiefmat.titel: Stukken betreffende de bemoeiingen van de Staten-Generaal met de geschillen tussen de Societeit van Suriname en de W.I.C. over de slechte staat van de verdedigingswerken in Suriname
archiefmat.titel_eng: Documents regarding the intervention of the States-General on account of the dispute between the Society of Surinam and the WIC concerning the poor condition of the defences of Suriname
archiefmat.notes: The file contains copies of documents from the period 1684-1711.
